text: Reanimatsioon [Reanimation] is the third album by Estonian punk rock band Singer Vinger and the first to be released on CD. == Track listing == #"Massikommunikatsioon '84" [Mass communication] (Hardi Volmer) #"Mida ma näen" [What do I see] (Volmer) #"Sängselg silm" [Bedback eye] (Roald Jürlau/Villu Kangur) #"Jumalaga puberteet" [Farewell puberty] (Volmer) #"Kodusõda" [Civil war; lit: home war (wordplay in the song)] (Jürlau/Kangur) #"Faatum" [Fate] (Jürlau/Kangur) #"Makulatuur" [Scrap paper] (Volmer) #"Sirts oli sire" [Sirts was willowy] (Ramones/Volmer) #"Born to Be Mild" (Volmer) #"Ära jahtu" [Don't cool down] (Volmer) #"Kalkar" [Bum] (Jürlau/Volmer) #"Massikommunikatsioon '95" (Volmer) Category:1995 albums Category:Singer Vinger albums Category:Estonian-language albums
title: Reanimatsioon
